Redistribution
--------------

Redistribution of the Kiro binary is not permitted outside the terms
set by AWS. For that reason:

  * rato-verlay does NOT host or mirror the Kiro tarball. The ebuild
    fetches the tarball directly from AWS's public distribution
    endpoint at build time.
  * The dev-util/kiro-bin ebuild carries
    RESTRICT="strip mirror bindist" so that Gentoo mirrors and
    binhosts do not attempt to redistribute either the distfile or
    any binpkg derived from it.

